        <updateDate>2021-07-12T17:16:28Z</updateDate>
        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Fire Fauci Act</strong></p> <p>This bill reduces the annual rate of pay of the Director of the National Institute of Allergy and Infectious Diseases (NIAID) to $0. This reduction applies until there is a new director who is not Anthony Fauci, MD.</p> <p>In addition, the Government Accountability Office must audit digital correspondence, policy memoranda, and financial transactions of the Office of the Director of NIAID from October 1, 2019, through December 31, 2021.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
